name: Sorus III
description:
Sorus III is the third piece in a new series that continues in exploring the microscopic world. These artworks have been crafted with thoughtful insight and tender loving care. On a technical level, they mix home-brewed generative systems with hand-drawn images using Processing and GANs. 

Size : 3508x4961px PNG [bitmap image]
